HelpTooltip:
ABOUT 
 This node calculates the differences between the first input and the second input/s and outputs the distance value in an array of floats. First Input port and Second Input port connect to a Feature Extractor or a Datatype node. Both inputs must be of the same type.
PortTooltip: Connect a Feature Extractor or Data Type node
Connect a Feature Extractor or Data Type node
Connect to Serial Vector. Outputs an array of float values.

tips: Float value/s of distance between inputs
